data.description: This single level ranch style home is a cozy and welcoming space that has recently undergone some exciting updates. With three bedrooms and one bathroom, it is a perfect size for a small family or group of roommates. The new flooring adds a fresh and modern touch, while the freshly painted walls create a clean and inviting atmosphere throughout. The updated stove and cabinets in the kitchen are both stylish and functional, providing ample storage and cooking space for all your culinary needs. Outside, the covered carport offers convenient shelter for your vehicle, while the spacious front and back yard provide plenty of room to relax, play, and entertain guests. Whether you're looking for a peaceful retreat or a lively gathering spot, this home has everything you need to make it your own.
